{"name":"HTML","permalink":"http://lingyu.life/tags/HTML/","url":"/async/tags/HTML.json","count":17,"_total":17,"_totalPage":2,"_page":2,"posts":[{"tags":[{"name":"CSS","permalink":"http://lingyu.life/tags/CSS/","url":"/async/tags/CSS.json","count":22},{"name":"HTML","permalink":"http://lingyu.life/tags/HTML/","url":"/async/tags/HTML.json","count":17}],"categories":[{"name":"翻译","permalink":"http://lingyu.life/categories/%E7%BF%BB%E8%AF%91/","url":"/async/categories/翻译.json","count":10}],"url":"/async/posts/2014/05/19/google-responsive-design-fundamentals.json","date":1400428800000,"path":{"year":2014,"month":5,"day":19,"name":"google-responsive-design-fundamentals"},"subtitle":"翻译自谷歌Web开发最佳实践手册","title":"响应式Web设计基础","permalink":"http://lingyu.life/2014/05/19/google-responsive-design-fundamentals/","content":"<p>本文所有内容来自<a href=\"https://developers.google.com/web/fundamentals/documentation/multi-device-layouts/rwd-fundamentals\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Responsive Web Design Fundamentals</a></p>\n<p>手机、大屏手机、平板电脑、桌面电脑、游戏控制台、电视、甚至是可穿戴设备，如此多的设备也形成了多种多样的屏幕尺寸。屏幕的大小总在变，我们需要我们的网页今后能够适应任何屏幕尺寸</p>"},{"tags":[{"name":"CSS","permalink":"http://lingyu.life/tags/CSS/","url":"/async/tags/CSS.json","count":22},{"name":"HTML","permalink":"http://lingyu.life/tags/HTML/","url":"/async/tags/HTML.json","count":17}],"categories":[{"name":"翻译","permalink":"http://lingyu.life/categories/%E7%BF%BB%E8%AF%91/","url":"/async/categories/翻译.json","count":10}],"url":"/async/posts/2014/05/04/google-style-guide.json","date":1399132800000,"path":{"year":2014,"month":5,"day":4,"name":"google-style-guide"},"subtitle":"写更简洁、更美观的HTML和CSS","title":"Google的HTML/CSS样式指南","permalink":"http://lingyu.life/2014/05/04/google-style-guide/","content":"<p>之前读过网易的NEC，以及百度的前端编码规范，感觉自己HTML和CSS代码写的很烂，这里又读了一下Google的style guide，发现有很多地方值得学习补充，在这里大致上翻译一下</p>"},{"tags":[{"name":"CSS","permalink":"http://lingyu.life/tags/CSS/","url":"/async/tags/CSS.json","count":22},{"name":"JavaScript","permalink":"http://lingyu.life/tags/JavaScript/","url":"/async/tags/JavaScript.json","count":28},{"name":"HTML","permalink":"http://lingyu.life/tags/HTML/","url":"/async/tags/HTML.json","count":17},{"name":"思考","permalink":"http://lingyu.life/tags/%E6%80%9D%E8%80%83/","url":"/async/tags/思考.json","count":1}],"categories":[{"name":"思考总结","permalink":"http://lingyu.life/categories/%E6%80%9D%E8%80%83%E6%80%BB%E7%BB%93/","url":"/async/categories/思考总结.json","count":3}],"url":"/async/posts/2014/09/22/learn-fe.json","date":1411315200000,"path":{"year":2014,"month":9,"day":22,"name":"learn-fe"},"subtitle":"一些总结","title":"学前端的一点总结","permalink":"http://lingyu.life/2014/09/22/learn-fe/","content":"<p>最近<a href=\"https://github.com/qiu-deqing\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Qiu</a>开了一个<a href=\"https://github.com/qiu-deqing/FE-learning/blob/master/README.md\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">FE学习经验介绍</a>，并邀请我去写一点东西。感觉这种方式很有意思，趁着闲下来了，就随便扯了一些，希望能帮到想学前端的同学。我自己只是个前端初学者，希望能有更多的前端爱好者一同学习探讨~~</p>"},{"tags":[{"name":"CSS","permalink":"http://lingyu.life/tags/CSS/","url":"/async/tags/CSS.json","count":22},{"name":"JavaScript","permalink":"http://lingyu.life/tags/JavaScript/","url":"/async/tags/JavaScript.json","count":28},{"name":"HTML","permalink":"http://lingyu.life/tags/HTML/","url":"/async/tags/HTML.json","count":17}],"categories":[{"name":"性能优化","permalink":"http://lingyu.life/categories/%E6%80%A7%E8%83%BD%E4%BC%98%E5%8C%96/","url":"/async/categories/性能优化.json","count":5}],"url":"/async/posts/2014/03/25/performance-2.json","date":1395676800000,"path":{"year":2014,"month":3,"day":25,"name":"performance-2"},"subtitle":"前端性能优化系列","title":"前端性能优化（JavaScript篇）","permalink":"http://lingyu.life/2014/03/25/performance-2/","content":"<p>最近准备笔试面试题的时候看到很多关于前端性能优化的问题，所以提前调研做做准备，加上我之前写的两篇博客，组成一个新系列</p>"},{"tags":[{"name":"CSS","permalink":"http://lingyu.life/tags/CSS/","url":"/async/tags/CSS.json","count":22},{"name":"JavaScript","permalink":"http://lingyu.life/tags/JavaScript/","url":"/async/tags/JavaScript.jso